.TH vdf_get_bool 3

.SH NAME
vdf_get_bool

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

int vdf_get_bool(const VDFNode *object, const char *key, int fallback);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Look up a direct child of `object` by key and interpret it as a boolean.

Interprets "0" as false and any other valid integer string as true.
If the child is not found or is not a valid integer string, returns `fallback`.

.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns 0 or 1, or `fallback`.

.SH ERRORS
None.

